dct_description_sm: Pictorial relief. Illustration of Windsor Castle across top of map. Also included is a list of the first members of the Order of the Garter. Verso: Description of Berskshire and index. "Cum privilegio." From: The theatre of the empire of Great Britaine ... / divided and described by Iohn Speed. London : And are to be solde by I. Sudbury and G. Humble, 1611.
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : are to be solde in Popes head Alley by I. Sud. and Georg Humble, [1610]
